name: Master Of Impossible Tracks
description:
Master Of Impossible Tracks is all about balance and control, don't let the bike get out of balance or you are crashed to death, don't let the bike speed get too slow or too fast and you are down to death.

Features
> Purpose built well of death like real
> World class adventurous environment
> Excellent bike control for this stunt game
> Unique Camera angles to view deathly shots
